org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.encoded

Class IoTrace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.io.orc.encoded.IoTrace

  • public final class IoTrace
extends Object
    Single threaded IO trace. Note: this can be made MTT merely by using an AtomicInteger, and storing a thread ID.
